org.openehealth.ipf.commons.ihe.xds.core.ebxml

Interface EbXMLRegistryObject

  • All Superinterfaces:
    EbXMLSlotList
    All Known Subinterfaces:
    EbXMLAssociation, EbXMLExtrinsicObject, EbXMLRegistryPackage
    All Known Implementing Classes:
    EbXMLAssociation21, EbXMLAssociation30, EbXMLExtrinsicObject21, EbXMLExtrinsicObject30, EbXMLRegistryObject21, EbXMLRegistryObject30, EbXMLRegistryPackage21, EbXMLRegistryPackage30

    public interface EbXMLRegistryObject
extends EbXMLSlotList
    Encapsulation of the ebXML classes for RegistryEntryType and RegistryObjectType.

    This class contains convenience methods and provides a version independent abstraction of the ebXML data structure.

    Author:
    Jens Riemschneider
